title: Pierre-Auguste Renoir 2024 Mini Wall Calendar
description:
Twelve gorgeous paintings by Impressionist painter, Pierre-Auguste Renoir. Known for his beautiful portrait and landscape paintings, this calendar is sure to please.

  • Dimensions: 7 x 7 in.
  • Includes major international holidays, lunar phases, and zodiac signs
  • Features 7 languages: Italian, English, German, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Japanese
